FBIS4-53236 "dreas096_c_94003" FBIS-EAS-94-096 Daily Report 17 May 1994 North Korea Call for Probe Into Kwangju Incident Reported Call for Probe Into Kwangju Incident Reported SK1705054294 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0524 GMT 17 May 94 SK1705054294 Pyongyang KCNA English BFN [Text] Pyongyang, May 17 (KCNA) -- The national committee for inheritance of the spirit of the May 18 Kwangju popular uprising and probe into the truth in South Korea published a statement on May 14, demanding probe into the truth behind the Kwangju massacre in May 1980, according to a radio report from Seoul. The committee urged the Kim Yong-sam group to amend the "special law" on the Kwangju incident at an early date and make a strict investigation into the principal culprits of the Kwangju massacre.
